    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, this unit features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the dual-VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates. The chassis remains taut, utilizing the original M-variable differential lock and McPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no rock chips or oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. A collector-quality example with a fully documented service dossier.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
