      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with how smooth it is!",
