      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The powertrain delivers a seamless surge to an 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral grip. This example has been meticulously preserved, featuring comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and tight, while the factory-spec suspension maintains the chassis's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. From the pristine underside to the flawless throttle response, this vehicle operates with the exactitude of a showroom-fresh machine.",
